    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 1</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You summon terrible images, memories and thoughts within your mind to trigger a controlled breakdown, which allows you to immediately enter your Blazing Rage, but causes you to suffer a -2 penalty to saves against Fear effects for the duration of the Rage (or Kyuubi Manifestation), plus 1d4 minutes afterward.<br><br>Once the Rage ends, you suffer 1 temporary Charisma damage (Will DC 16 negates).</p>\n\n\n\n",
